		<title>Do-It-Yourself Solar Panels – Electricity Conversion From Sunlight</title>
		<link>http://www.diysolarpanelsworld.com/do-it-yourself-solar-panels-%e2%80%93-electricity-conversion-from-sunlight</link>
		<comments>http://www.diysolarpanelsworld.com/do-it-yourself-solar-panels-%e2%80%93-electricity-conversion-from-sunlight#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Thu, 10 May 2012 22:02:37 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator>admin</dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[Solar Panels Electricity]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Electrical Items]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Electricity Conversion]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Electromagnetic Radiation]]></category>
